            <lg xml:id="TK1326">
<l>uṇaliṉu muṇṭa taṟaliṉitu kāmam </l>
<l>puṇartali ṉūṭa liṉitu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To digest what has been eaten is more delightful than to eat more likewise love is more delightful in dislike than intercourse.</l>
